=================================================================
               Czech Text Document Corpus v 1.0
=================================================================

BASIC INFORMATION
--------------------
Czech Text Document Corpus v 1.0 contains 11.995 Czech newspaper articles provided by the Czech News Agency (CTK, http://www.ctk.eu/). The articles are annotated by the labels selected from the 60 categories.

This corpus is available only for research purposes for free. Commercial use in any form is strictly excluded. 

For further information about the corpus, you can see the attached paper below:

@inproceedings{hrala2013evaluation,
  title={Evaluation of the Document Classification Approaches},
  author={Hrala, Michal and Kr{\'a}l, Pavel},
  booktitle={Proceedings of the 8th International Conference on Computer Recognition Systems CORES 2013},
  pages={877--885},
  year={2013},
  organization={Springer}
}

Please, cite this paper when you used these texts in the experiments.

AUTHORS
